 === monoModuleLoader ===
    + design a mono (C#) library that wraps the pplt-core.
    + also build a mono module loader to load modules written
      in C# or so...

 === Use of QT ===
    + Use only QT based thread stuff to be more or less platform independent.
      At first the module locking!
    + Use QT based XML stuff (later)
    + Define interfaceses and implement a module loader for Qt plugins. 
